udies of such systems will drastically\nimprove our understanding of the relation between cluster mergers and cooling,\nand how these fit in the bigger picture of active galactic nuclei (AGN)\nfeedback.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jan 2021 19:00:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-27"}
