ic Eigen cation as the most prevalent hydrated proton\nspecies in acid solutions of dilute to moderate concentrations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 5 Jan 2021 21:04:05 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-07"}
