ults\nshow possible significant and coherent sex-specific risk markers of different\nACS sub-populations by interpreting ML mortality models trained on EHRs.\nDifferences are observed in the identified risk markers between women and men,\nhighlighting the importance of considering sex-specific markers in implementing\nmore appropriate treatment strategies and better clinical outcomes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jan 2021 00:56:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 4 Oct 2021 17:31:32 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Nov 2021 20:13:46 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-11-19"}
