ser. Simulation\nresults show that the proposed detection algorithms exhibit superior\nperformance-complexity trade-off over the existing detection techniques in\nMBM-mMIMO systems.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jan 2021 07:49:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-01-07"}
