PO in Maple for the case of plane and space\ncurves. Our experiments illustrate its practical nature.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Jan 2021 08:48:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 17 Feb 2022 17:26:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-02-18"}
